#: includes/modules/TableMakerItem/TableMakerItem.php:534
msgid ""
"Here you can enter content for this column’s rows. Rows are numbered for "
"your convenience – one row in this editor equals one row in the table. "
"Content can included HTML markup, which means characters such as &quot; "
"&apos; &amp; &lt; &gt; will need to be avoided or escaped in order to avoid "
"errors. Here, individual row cells can be styled and icons, buttons and "
"images added using tags which are unique to this module. See documentation "
"for details."
